cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SI. 

The paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for summarization of meeting speeches. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses word embeddings and graph degeneracy, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) and designing custom diversity and informativeness measures, which are relevant to social and information networks (cs.SI).
